duties_responsibilities.duty: Lead multiple architectural projects simultaneously, ensuring coordination and completion of construction documentation.
Utilize Revit, AutoCAD, and Sketchup to design and develop architectural plans and drawings.
Provide technical expertise in coordination and completion of construction documentation.
Cultivate a team spirit and demonstrate leadership qualities within the architectural team.
Maintain effective communication with clients, contractors, and the architectural team.
Collaborate with diverse team members to achieve precise attention to detail and client service.
